               <P>The successful bidder will be required to have in place:</P>
               <P>— BS-EN ISO 9001 or equivalent.</P>
               <P>— BS 7499 or equivalent.</P>
               <P>— BS 7858 or equivalent.</P>
               <P>— SIA Approved Contractor Status.</P>
